<tr>
<td width="600" colspan="4">
<b>Description</b><br>
This item is created by using the smithing trade skill. Combine the following items in the Royal Freeport Forge located only in Freeport, to create the Seafarer Buckler. 
<br><br>
<li> Buckler mold
<li> Smithy hammer
<li> Flask of water
<li> High quality sheet of metal </td>
